According to the testimony of the latter, he had to look at bed-and-breakfasts and restaurants.
He asked for an invoice for his consumption there, which was then modelled on the invoices to be submitted to the applications of the Ministry of Youth and Sports, the Ministry of Social Affairs and Labour and the Municipality of Budapest.
These were mostly written by István Lados and his partner, András <0xC5><0x90>ri, who, according to our information, wrote mostly the reports necessary for obtaining the grants.
