For example, the forgers did not pay attention to the fact that the Ny<0xC3><0xAD>regyháza HIB Kft. was under liquidation at the time (2001) when the group of the Young City Association was eating there, which is why the liquidator of the company – as far as we know – denied that he had issued the paper.
Consciously Presented
